headline: ROL Q2 Deep Dive: M&A Integration, Commercial Growth, and Margin Focus Shape Outlook
summary: Pest control company Rollins (NYSE:ROL) reported revenue ahead of Wall Street’s expectations in Q2 CY2025, with sales up 12.1% year on year to $999.5 million. Its non-GAAP profit of $0.30 per share was in line with analysts’ consensus estimates.
